headline: Phillips 66 Issues Letter to Shareholders
summary: HOUSTON, May 19, 2025--Phillips 66 today sent a letter to shareholders highlighting the key issues on the ballot at its Annual Meeting on May 21.

headline: Phillips 66 (PSX) Sells Majority Stake in European Fuel Retailer
